    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1943-07-21T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1943-07-21T00:00:00-05:00" n="174"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d174">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">Roosevelt Papers: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">President <persName type="from">Roosevelt</persName> to Prime
                        Minister <persName type="to">Churchill</persName>
                    </hi>
                    <note n="1" xml:id="d174fn1">Sent to the United States Naval Attaché, London,
                        via Navy channels.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">secret</hi>
                        <lb/>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">priority</hi>
                    </seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">[<placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>,] <date calendar="gregorian" when="1943-07-21">July 21,
                            1943</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Number 320 personal and secret from the President for the <gloss target="#t_FNP1"
                        >Former Naval Person</gloss>.</p>
                <p>Referring to your numbers 371 and 372,<note n="2" xml:id="d174fn2">
                        <hi rend="italic">Ante</hi>, <ref target="#pg_393">pp. 393</ref>, <ref
                            target="#pg_394">394</ref>.</note> in consideration of the fact that so
                    far I have had no word from <gloss target="#t_UJ1">UJ</gloss> though I have
                    wired him, I am in agreement with your suggestion that the “<gloss
                        target="#t_Quadrant1">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Quadrant</hi>
                    </gloss>” conference be started about August fifteenth in the location of
                    Montcalm.</p>
                <p>Please inform me as early as possible of exact date of meeting that will suit
                    your arrangements for transportation. If <gloss target="#t_UJ1">UJ</gloss> moves
                    I think August seventeenth would suit me better.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Roosevelt</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
